OL,3,CFuneral held for 'lovely boy' who was
OL,4,Cstabbed to death on Woolwich bus
OL,6,FThe mother of a 14-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fwas stabbed to death on a bus in
OL,8,FWoolwich earlier this year, has said
OL,9,Fhis death could have been prevented,
OL,10,Fas his funeral was held on Wednesday.
OL,12,FKelyan Bokassa was stabbed around 27
OL,13,Ftimes as he travelled home on a route
OL,14,F472 bus in Woolwich Church Street on
OL,15,FJanuary 7.
OL,17,FHis mother Marie Bokassa said she
OL,18,Fwanted ITV News London at his funeral
OL,19,Fin Greenwich, so people could see the
OL,20,Fdevastating impact of knife crime on
OL,21,Fhis family, friends and the community.
