OL,3,CFuneral held for 'lovely boy' who was
OL,4,Cstabbed to death on Woolwich bus
OL,6,FSpeaking after the service, Ms Bokassa
OL,7,Fpaid tribute to her son: "Kelyan was a
OL,8,Flovely boy ... it's hard for me to
OL,9,Ftalk about it because I lost my son
OL,10,Fand I still can't believe it.
OL,12,F"He was a very, very loyal friend ...
OL,13,FI miss him so much."
OL,15,FShe went on to say that she believed
OL,16,Fthe teenager, who was an aspiring
OL,17,Frapper, was "let down by the system".
OL,19,F"I have on many occasions tried to
OL,20,Fhelp my son and I was denied any form
OL,21,Fof support.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
