OL,3,CFuneral held for 'lovely boy' who was
OL,4,Cstabbed to death on Woolwich bus
OL,6,F"Although there (were) organisations
OL,7,Fwho could have prevented him being
OL,8,Fgroomed ... the local authority did
OL,9,Fnot engage with those organisations,"
OL,10,Fshe said.
OL,12,FExplaining that Kelyan had been placed
OL,13,Finto care, Ms Bokassa added: "I have
OL,14,Fno idea why they didn't want me to
OL,15,Flook after my son, but I was a better
OL,16,Foption than the streets looking after
OL,17,Fhim.
OL,19,F"So I feel extremely, extremely upset
OL,20,Fbecause this could have been
OL,21,Fprevented."
