OL,3,CFuneral held for 'lovely boy' who was
OL,4,Cstabbed to death on Woolwich bus
OL,6,FKelyan was killed just months after
OL,7,Fhis friend Daejuan Campbell was also
OL,8,Fstabbed to death.
OL,10,FDaejaun, 15, was killed in Eglinton
OL,11,FRoad, Woolwich, on 22 September 2024,
OL,12,Fless than a mile and a half away from
OL,13,Fwhere Kelyan was killed.
OL,15,FThe Metropolitan Police said that no
OL,16,Flinks have been established between
OL,17,Fthe two deaths.
