OL,3,CFuneral held for 'lovely boy' who was
OL,4,Cstabbed to death on Woolwich bus
OL,6,FMs Bokassa said: "He has been exposed
OL,7,Fto other kids who passed ... when I
OL,8,Fwas growing up, I've never had to bury
OL,9,Fa friend, but now it's like they have
OL,10,Fto do it on a daily, nearly on a
OL,11,Fdaily, weekly basis. It's very scary."
OL,13,FTwo boys, aged 15 and 16, have been
OL,14,Fcharged with Kelyan's murder.
OL,16,FA plea hearing has been set for April
OL,17,F14 and a provisional trial at the Old
OL,18,FBailey from October 13.
